         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office, ¶ Melbourne, 17 April 1882.  ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor by direction of the Chief Secretary to request that you will furnish information on the following points, viz: ¶  ¶ ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.04.17b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 2972, pp. 1196-7, unit 60, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office of Victoria</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Circular sent to nine sub-departments within the Chief Secretary's Department.</p>
               </note>Chief Secretary's Office,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 17 April 1882. </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor by direction of the Chief Secretary to request that you will furnish information on the following points, viz:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1 The number of classified officers in your department.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>2 The number of third schedule officers in your department.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>3 The numbers of all other persons employed whether paid from a vote for salaries or from a contingency vote.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>T. R. Wilson<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For reply, see M to J. Grant, 18 April 1882.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">The Government Botanist</p>
         </div>
